                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8858" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0404</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1542 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杂交优势：“一带一路”征程上中尽国际混合型组织的生发与变革</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hybrid Vigor: The Emergence and Transformation of Zhongjin International&#39;s Hybrid Organization on the &quot;Belt and Road&quot; Journey</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘平青，史溢文，刘园园，刘东旭，霍春阳，王志鹏，王瀛</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中尽国际控股集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“一带一路”；组织变革；组织模式；混合型组织</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Belt and Road&quot;, Organizational Transformation, Organizational Model, Hybrid Organization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在“一带一路”倡议的浪潮中，中尽国际控股集团有限公司（简称中尽国际）作为中央党校控股的国有企业，不仅面临着将理论研究成果转化为实际经济活动的挑战，更需要在海外市场上克服文化差异、属地化难题等多重障碍。本案例原汁原味记录了中尽国际萌芽期、分蘖期、拔节期和抽穗期的发展历程，再现了中尽国际在“一带一路”征程中的探索与变革。通过混合组织职能、混合组织框架、混合平台建设，中尽国际不仅在国内市场找到了发展路径，更在海外市场取得了显著成就，成功实施了多个公共社会性服务项目，展示了国有企业的责任与担当。本案例旨在向学员展示企业如何发挥“杂交优势”，通过建设混合型组织而实现国际化发展与社会责任的双赢，以及如何在“一带一路”倡议中贡献中国智慧和力量。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the wave of the &quot;Belt and Road&quot; initiative, China Zhongjin International Holdings Group Co., Ltd. (referred to as Zhongjin International), as a state-owned enterprise controlled by the Party School of the CPC central committee, not only faces the challenge of transforming theoretical research results into practical economic activities, but also needs to overcome multiple obstacles such as cultural differences and localization difficulties in overseas markets. This case study authentically records the development process of Zhongjin International in its budding, branching, branching, and heading stages, reproducing its exploration and transformation in the  &quot;Belt and Road&quot; journey. Through the construction of hybrid organizational functions, hybrid organizational framework and hybrid platform, Zhongjin International has not only found a development path in the domestic market, but also achieved significant success in overseas markets, successfully implementing multiple public social service projects, demonstrating the responsibility and commitment of state-owned enterprises. This case aims to show how enterprises can leverage &quot;hybrid advantages&quot; to achieve win-win situations in international development and social responsibility through the construction of hybrid organizations, and how to contribute Chinese wisdom and strength to the &quot;Belt and Road&quot; initiative.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">混合型组织</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
